1e:T44c,Kontur creates web services that make business life easier.

Owned full-cycle hiring for 7–10 technical vacancies simultaneously: from market and profile analysis to candidate offer and onboarding

Candidate profiles included DevOps, Linux/System Engineers, C#/BI Developers, QA (manual/auto), PMs, and more.

Tools: HH.ru, AmazingHiring, podbor.io, Telegram, LinkedIn, Habr, Boolean search, X-Ray

Internal projects
- Revised the methodology for collecting feedback on the hiring process, developed a transparent and efficient vacancy management process for customers, created SLO for DB developers, described target vacancy closure times, alternative sources, and hiring process.
- Acted as a reviewer for a colleague, learning to properly evaluate candidates, ask questions, and determine grades.

Key results
- 95% probation period pass rate.
- 26 days time to offer for C# developers.
- Conducted 336 interviews in 2024.
- Simultaneously handled up to 10 different profiles (testers, administrators, Linux engineers, Ceph, virtualization, network, project managers, webinar specialists, etc.).13: [
